<h3>An Afternoon of Incidental Noise</h3>
<h4>January 28th, 2017</h4>
<a href="../img/2016-2017/incidental.jpg"><img src="../img/2016-2017/incidental-thumb.jpg"/></a>
<a href="../img/2016-2017/incidental.jpg"><img src="../img/2016-2017/incidental-thumb.jpg"/></a>
<a href="../img/2016-2017/incidental.jpg"><img src="../img/2016-2017/incidental-thumb.jpg"/></a>
